396
00:24:16,830 --> 00:24:18,340
So cute...

397
00:24:23,520 --> 00:24:25,400
Y-Yes?

398
00:24:33,780 --> 00:24:35,590
Thirsty...

399
00:24:35,590 --> 00:24:37,020
Wait, I...

400
00:24:38,410 --> 00:24:40,830
already... started on that.

401
00:24:47,340 --> 00:24:50,170
Nothing beats yogurt in the morning!

402
00:24:50,170 --> 00:24:52,590
Yeah, I agree.

403
00:24:52,590 --> 00:24:56,240
