408
00:25:10,250 --> 00:25:11,210
We're coming in!

409
00:25:11,210 --> 00:25:13,180
W-Wait a sec!

410
00:25:13,180 --> 00:25:15,180
What is it? What happâ€”

411
00:25:16,760 --> 00:25:18,750
It's not what it looks like!

412
00:25:18,750 --> 00:25:21,950
When I woke up, she was sleeping next to me, andâ€”

413
00:25:24,070 --> 00:25:27,890
Since my futon's not here yet, I borrowed his.

414
00:25:27,890 --> 00:25:29,790
Wait, that's why?

415
00:25:38,640 --> 00:25:41,430
Okay, I'll go first, then.

416
00:25:41,710 --> 00:25:43,740
I'm Nanako Kogure!

417
00:25:43,740 --> 00:25:45,600
I'm originally from Shiga Prefecture!

418
00:25:45,600 --> 00:25:47,310
You can call me Nanako!

419
00:25:47,310 --> 00:25:48,940
Nice to meet you.

420
00:25:49,400 --> 00:25:51,820
She seems kinda popular, maybe a bit of a gyaru.

421
00:25:51,820 --> 00:25:54,990
Let me guess: it was art school or a life of crimeâ€”

422
00:25:56,030 --> 00:25:58,590
You've got a talent for being a pain in the ass

423
00:25:58,590 --> 00:26:01,530
