424
00:26:01,530 --> 00:26:05,570
Let's not make fun of her, then.

425
00:26:05,570 --> 00:26:08,720
I'm Tsurayuki Rokuonji...

426
00:26:08,720 --> 00:26:10,420
I guess I'll keep it casual, too.

427
00:26:10,420 --> 00:26:13,290
That's a cool family name!

428
00:26:13,290 --> 00:26:14,260
